Name: DOWNWIND DIRECTION IN DEGREES
Explanation: THE VALUE OF 999 CAN BE USED TO INDICATE A VARIABLE WIND DIRECTION.

Name: THREAT ANGLE
Explanation: THE ZONE ANGLE IN DEGREES ON EITHER SIDE OF THE THREAT DIRECTION.

Name: LEFT AREA BOUNDARY IN DEGREES
Explanation: THE LEFT HAND BEARING LIMIT OF A SECTOR

Name: RIGHT AREA BOUNDARY IN DEGREES
Explanation: THE RIGHT HAND BEARING LIMIT OF A SECTOR

Name: ZONE ANGLE IN DEGREES
Explanation: THE ANGLE ON EITHER SIDE OF AN AXIS OR CENTER BEARING THAT DESCRIBES A ZONE THE SHAPE OF A PIECE OF PIE.

Name: WAVE BREAKER ANGLE
Explanation: DESCRIBES THE ACUTE ANGLE, IN DEGREES, FORMED BETWEEN THE BREAKER LINES AND THE SHORELINE.

Name: DIVE ANGLE OF ATTACK
Explanation: THE DIVE ANGLE OF ATTACK AT TIME OF RELEASE MEASURED IN DEGREES (0 DEGREES IS LEVEL FLIGHT AND 90 DEGREES IS STRAIGHT DOWN).

Name: IMPACT AZIMUTH
Explanation: THE IMPACT AZIMUTH OF THE SPECIFIED WEAPON.
